  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You generate a Bose-Einstein Condensate field around your armor that acts to entangle incoming attacks on a quantum level. You gain 5 temporary hit points for the duration. If a creature hits you with a melee attack while you have these hit points, the creature takes 5 cold damage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>At Higher Levels. When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, both the temporary hit points and the cold damage increase by 5 for each slot.</p>",
